    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>farfalle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> </strong>farfalle for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the farfalle, reserving 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
