    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> with the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water </strong>– this is your <strong>harissa stock</strong></p>",
